{"tid":219178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓:中方不再把北韓視為戰略資產","createTime":"2017-04-27T04:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T12:40:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c50b9fe32788e2a2e0198d58972bf76f98f584f","tid":219178,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/04/25/1548169_832e32f1e384f6ad24ebab0e6c7679af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F1548169_832e32f1e384f6ad24ebab0e6c7679af.jpg&h=15cc47d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於中國政府和媒體相繼向北韓釋出反對新一輪挑釁的訊號，南韓外交部發言人趙俊赫表示，這標誌中國對北韓的態度發生變化，即中國不再把平壤政府視為戰略資產，而視為「負債」。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社引述趙俊赫指出，北韓以非法手段開發核與導彈，對朝鮮半島及地區局勢構成嚴重威脅，中方就此向北韓釋放強烈的警告訊號。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人耿爽周一回應中方對北韓核試所持立場的提問時表示，目前朝鮮半島局勢複雜敏感，高度緊張，強烈敦促有關各方保持冷靜克制，不要採取使局勢緊張升級的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n中國《環球時報》早前也發表社評稱，如果北韓在本月再破底線，中國將會願意看到安理會做出包括嚴格限制對北韓出口石油的空前嚴厲措施。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1548169/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%3A%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%8A%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1548169%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%253A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258A%258A%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2595%25A5%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4osQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=0b57066b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1548169/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%3A%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%8A%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2</a>"},{"pid":"ed6ebac45b13b434e04673c60e1750d8e9d1c026","tid":219178,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"咁